{"tid":2218770,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"香港不再 安穩如初 祈求各位 留存希望 香港可再 安穩來過","createTime":"2020-09-26T12:37:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T12:37:30.000Z","uid":258822,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6fb5fbd9e22afc832e16ce47189ed0c445fa255b","tid":2218770,"uid":258822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T12:37:30.000Z","msg":"早排喺903 聽到呢首覺得幾正<br />\n之後上youtube搵翻 睇翻啲歌詞先知咁痴線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《半島 》<br />\n<br />\n曲: YUSOBEIT<br />\n詞: YU<br />\n編: YUSOBEIT/Abby Cheung<br />\n監: Abby Cheung<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">紅</span>日未照 燈火正燒<br />\n<span class=\"red\">人</span>城內裡 喜歡通宵<br />\n<span class=\"red\">頭</span>從來未昏 腳亦從未軟<br />\n<span class=\"red\">來</span>撐著半島的溫暖<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">難</span>為尚有 幾多帳單<br />\n<span class=\"red\">圍</span>牆內裡 不少劫難<br />\n<span class=\"red\">本</span>著那獅子氣無懼無怕<br />\n<span class=\"red\">土</span>釀出希望的眼<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">香</span>滿地靠百家炊火<br />\n<span class=\"red\">港</span>載盛了多少收穫<br />\n<span class=\"red\">不</span>安與難過終需離座<br />\n<span class=\"red\">再</span>差也可抱擁這暖窩<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">安</span>坐在那幸福小島<br />\n<span class=\"red\">穩</span>躺在狂風的旅途上<br />\n<span class=\"red\">如</span>臨大敵也當他<br />\n<span class=\"red\">初</span>哥<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">祈</span>願是 馬與舞蹈長熱<br />\n<span class=\"red\">求</span>大運 於風車中兜轉<br />\n<span class=\"red\">各</span>自各賭上信念來實踐<br />\n<span class=\"red\">位</span>置裡的擺位不變<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">留</span>著汗與國力磨鍊<br />\n<span class=\"red\">存</span>在為捍東方的標誌<br />\n<span class=\"red\">希</span>望有天子女能自由說<br />\n<span class=\"red\">望</span>會識講:<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">香</span>靠大眾擦起花火<br />\n<span class=\"red\">港</span>拍岸裡多少激浪<br />\n<span class=\"red\">可</span>惜與懷緬始終無助<br />\n<span class=\"red\">再</span>差也不致心死退夥<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">安</span>顧熱盼在半光的島<br />\n<span class=\"red\">穩</span>固地迎風一切如願<br />\n<span class=\"red\">來</span>年日月也會可<br />\n<span class=\"red\">過</span>一波<br />\n<br />\n來年日月也會可<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-qBewIH0HSI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-qBewIH0HSI&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu5B82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=2b548ff6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-qBewIH0HSI</a>"}]}